@startuml
[*] --> NavigationState
NavigationState --> ProjectInfoState : Select project
ProjectInfoState --> PhotoOrVideoState : View photos or videos
PhotoOrVideoState --> CareerOpportunityState : Go to career opportunities
CareerOpportunityState --> UpdateOrApplicationState : View updates or apply for job/internship
UpdateOrApplicationState --> JobApplicationSubmittedState : Submit job application
JobApplicationSubmittedState --> CheckSubmittedApplicationsState : Check submitted applications

@enduml
